地方原地跳60下，跟住做20個掌上壓。據說心跳加快之後，血液都會流得快d，咁你個腦就會以為你要做大單嘢而幫你開二段，即是所謂爆機mode，以依種形式去欺騙本來要休息既身體係短期會好有幫助，但係長期個腦會適應左就唔會俾你昆到就無用。所以樓主要珍惜機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運用之。"},{"pid":"76c9d43c7852fc265f9ecc539a0f74fcb5a120bd","tid":475234,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nno🍺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9491f6a1acbba693cbb72baf9b67856fbeaf97c","tid":475234,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食香蕉，食/飲朱古力。<br />\n據說可以提供70-90mins短暫能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補充返，食/飲朱古力可以拎大腦唔知生產一d咩拎到個人醒d同開心d。<br />\n<br />\n食香蕉原意係為飽腹之餘同時提供身體所需能量去支撐你之後既工作。<br />\n<br />\n之後你再搵個地方原地跳60下，跟住做20個掌上壓。據說心跳加快之後，血液都會流得快d，咁你個腦就會以為你要做大單嘢而幫你開二段，即是所謂爆機mode，以依種形式去欺騙本來要休息既身體係短期會好有幫助，但係長期個腦會適應左就唔會俾你昆到就無用。所以樓主要珍惜機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運用之。</blockquote><br />\nthx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要食條蕉再做嗰啲運動先會開爆機mode?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a08da089b8fd24c622aefe6ccc39fc4f1b74b7","tid":475234,"uid":40354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"冷泡茉莉綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70cfee993dfefde57475604d5dfd208262ec0b8","tid":475234,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"飲咖啡+1粒克痛。<br />\n包你爽"},{"pid":"46680c279bc014522387fe4319325d8ed4f0629a","tid":475234,"uid":32588,"like":0,"di